69
00:09:37,814 --> 00:09:40,717
Alam ko rin naman 'yan.

70
00:09:43,887 --> 00:09:45,822
Yung stalker mo...

71
00:09:47,223 --> 00:09:48,858
Pumunta ako sa lugar ko sa Seoul.

72
00:09:52,262 --> 00:09:53,263
Tinanong niya ako...

73
00:09:54,564 --> 00:09:56,032
