79
00:10:41,645 --> 00:10:42,912
Nagsimula siyang ma-bully.

80
00:10:46,850 --> 00:10:48,918
At hindi ko ito kayang tiisin nang mga sandaling iyon.

81
00:10:52,722 --> 00:10:54,090
Isa ang namatay,

82
